high_descs: Turn around and walk left to the shelves on the left wall.
Pick up the pencil on the top shelf all the way to the right.
Turn right and walk to the desk.
Place the pencil on the desk to the right of the book, parallel with the back of the desk chair.
Turn around and walk back to the shelves on the right.
Pick up the pencil on the bottom shelf.
Turn right and walk back to the desk.
Put the pencil on the desk on top of the other pencil.
anns.task_desc: Put two pencils on a desk.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wooden shelves on the left.
Pick up the pencil on the top shelf.
Turn right and walk to the white desk with the black chair.
Place the pencil on the white desk in front of the CD.
Turn around and walk back to the wooden shelves.
Pick up the yellow pencil from the second shelf.
Turn right and walk back to the white desk.
Put the pencil down on the desk next to the first yellow pencil.
anns.task_desc: To move two pencils from the shelves to the white desk.

high_descs: Back up and turn around, go forward and turn to the left, go forward to the shelf.
Pick up the pencil that is on the top shelf.
Turn around, go forward, then hang a left and go forward to the desk.
Put the pencil down on the desk in front of the chair.
Turn around, go forward past the boots, turn right and go forward to the shelves.
Pick up the pencil that is on the bottom shelf.
Turn around, go forward, then hang a left and go forward to the desk.
Put the pencil down on the desk behind the other pencil.
anns.task_desc: Put two pencils on a desk.
